I'm afraid it's going to be hard.

868
00:36:33,040 --> 00:36:34,080
I asked her about it yesterday.

869
00:36:34,200 --> 00:36:35,330
She hadn't found one yet.

870
00:36:36,290 --> 00:36:37,080
Hua Zhi

871
00:36:37,160 --> 00:36:38,530
