873
00:36:41,240 --> 00:36:42,120
Madam Hua,

874
00:36:42,200 --> 00:36:44,850
do you think this family school
is necessary?

875
00:36:45,200 --> 00:36:46,680
Judging by how hard she tries,

876
00:36:46,760 --> 00:36:47,680
