898
00:37:48,410 --> 00:37:50,530
Then, shall we keep trying tomorrow?

899
00:37:51,040 --> 00:37:51,640
Yes, we shall.

900
00:37:51,850 --> 00:37:52,810
Aren't there still

901
00:37:52,850 --> 00:37:54,040
