927
00:38:48,010 --> 00:38:49,330
Because our mother loved wearing them.

928
00:38:50,200 --> 00:38:51,560
She passed away many years ago.

929
00:38:52,530 --> 00:38:53,890
She must be very beautiful.

930
00:38:54,010 --> 00:38:55,080
