educate anyone well.

1039
00:42:33,080 --> 00:42:34,490
There's no grown man
left in that family.

1040
00:42:34,720 --> 00:42:36,640
What's so funny about that?

1041
00:42:37,080 --> 00:42:37,930
A family without a grown man

1042
00:42:37,970 --> 00:42:39,160
